{"tid":1103864,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[最後4場]#游蕙禎 黃心穎 彭慧中 黃翠如 陳嘉寶 湯怡 18-19 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽第31輪投選專區","createTime":"2019-04-12T16:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T14:49:30.000Z","uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5c9cc5a44ab21e76511bdcc3ae87eaffcfb57d8b","tid":1103864,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:29:27.000Z","msg":"以下為即將舉行之賽事<br />\n會員可留意稍後時間發出的比賽專用回覆並以回覆評分功能進行投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(唔識點樣用回覆評分功能黎投票既巴打可以參考下面既教學)<br />\n<br />\n由首場12:30am開始,每兩分鐘開賽一場<br />\n<br />\n朱晨麗 : 岑麗香<br />\n黃心穎 : 彭慧中<br />\n孫慧雪 : 袁澧林<br />\n陳煒 : 黃翠如<br />\n劉穎鏇 : 莊錠欣<br />\n陳嘉寶 : 陳庭欣<br />\n黃智雯 : 林泳淘<br />\n李施嬅 : 游蕙禎<br />\n湯怡 : 趙慧珊@SG<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hiNda68.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhiNda68.png&h=d4221617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/s2sfX8L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs2sfX8L.png&h=b53ffa65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冠聯第三十輪積分榜<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/WZrKXGs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FWZrKXGs.png&h=905dc7ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ffg4vwe7.png&d=%2FAErJKvlI7yUl6Jkpxfv8Phh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=bc943b47\" target=\"_blank\">http://i.imgur.com/fg4vwe7.png</a><br />\n有關主場指定額外得分情況,請參閱主場額外分數增幅表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db8c4a3df66c85f62e554d592874bdefca013f34","tid":1103864,"uid":92376,"like":68,"dislike":36,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-12T16:30:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-19 LIHKG香港冠軍女神聯賽第31輪</div><br 